    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a truly showroom-quality vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections, further protected by a professional ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin retains its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the dashboard is free of any UV damage or scratches. Mechanically, the car is flawless, boasting a comprehensive service history with every scheduled maintenance performed ahead of time at the dealership. It drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line\u2014tight, responsive, and quiet. Sale includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a thick folder of service records to provide the next owner with complete peace of mind.",
      "price": 44500.0,
